what's in mean_hp_by_cyl?
========================================================

```{r }
df_cars_db %>% 
  group_by( cyl) %>%
  summarize( avg = mean(hp),
             std = sd(hp) )  %>%
  show_query 
```
```
<SQL>
SELECT 
  `cyl`, 
  AVG(`hp`) AS `avg`, 
  STDEV(`hp`) AS `std`
FROM `df_cars`
GROUP BY `cyl`
```

automagic subqueries
========================================================

```{r }
df_cars_db %>% 
  group_by( cyl) %>%
  summarize( avg = mean(hp),
             std = sd(hp) )  %>%
  filter( avg > 100) %>%
  show_query 
```
```
<SQL>
SELECT *
FROM ( SELECT `cyl`, 
       AVG(`hp`) AS `avg`, 
       STDEV(`hp`) AS `std`
       FROM `df_cars`
       GROUP BY `cyl`
     )
WHERE (`avg` > 100.0)
```

