tbl_lazy & simulate_dbi
======================================================
```{r}
library(dbplyr)
data.frame(x = 1, y = 2) %>%
  tbl_lazy(src = simulate_sqlite()) ->
df_sqlite ## this is a lazy table

df_sqlite %>% 
  summarise(x = sd(x)) -> 
my_tbl_df

my_tbl_df %>%
  show_query()
```

